# Database Schema

## Tables

### users (extends Supabase auth.users)
```sql
- id: uuid (FK → auth.users.id)
- full_name: text NOT NULL
- specialty: text
- license_number: text
- organization_id: uuid (nullable, for teams)
- role: text DEFAULT 'clinician' CHECK (role IN ('clinician', 'admin', 'reviewer'))
- settings: jsonb DEFAULT '{}'
- created_at: timestamptz DEFAULT now()
- updated_at: timestamptz DEFAULT now()
```

### patients
```sql
- id: uuid PK DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- user_id: uuid FK → users.id NOT NULL
- mrn: text (medical record number, unique per user)
- full_name: text NOT NULL
- date_of_birth: date
- gender: text
- contact_info: jsonb DEFAULT '{}'
- ehr_patient_id: text (external EHR reference)
- created_at: timestamptz DEFAULT now()
- updated_at: timestamptz DEFAULT now()
```

### consultations
```sql
- id: uuid PK DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- user_id: uuid FK → users.id NOT NULL
- patient_id: uuid FK → patients.id (nullable)
- visit_type: text DEFAULT 'general'
- status: text DEFAULT 'scheduled' CHECK (status IN ('scheduled', 'recording', 'transcribed', 'note_generated', 'reviewed', 'finalized'))
- consent_given: boolean DEFAULT false
- consent_timestamp: timestamptz
- recording_duration_seconds: integer
- metadata: jsonb DEFAULT '{}'
- created_at: timestamptz DEFAULT now()
- updated_at: timestamptz DEFAULT now()
```

### transcripts
```sql
- id: uuid PK DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- consultation_id: uuid FK → consultations.id NOT NULL (UNIQUE)
- segments: jsonb NOT NULL DEFAULT '[]'
  -- Array of: {speaker: "doctor"|"patient", text: string, start_time: float, end_time: float, confidence: float}
- full_text: text (concatenated plain text for search)
- language: text DEFAULT 'en'
- provider: text DEFAULT 'deepgram' (transcription service used)
- created_at: timestamptz DEFAULT now()
- updated_at: timestamptz DEFAULT now()
```

### clinical_notes
```sql
- id: uuid PK DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- consultation_id: uuid FK → consultations.id NOT NULL
- template_id: uuid FK → note_templates.id
- sections: jsonb NOT NULL DEFAULT '[]'
  -- Array of: {title: string, content: string, order: number}
- billing_codes: jsonb DEFAULT '[]'
  -- Array of: {code: string, system: "ICD-10"|"CPT", description: string, confidence: float, accepted: boolean}
- status: text DEFAULT 'draft' CHECK (status IN ('draft', 'reviewed', 'finalized'))
- ai_model: text (model used for generation)
- generation_metadata: jsonb DEFAULT '{}'
- finalized_at: timestamptz
- finalized_by: uuid FK → users.id
- created_at: timestamptz DEFAULT now()
- updated_at: timestamptz DEFAULT now()
```

### note_templates
```sql
- id: uuid PK DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- user_id: uuid FK → users.id (NULL for system templates)
- name: text NOT NULL
- description: text
- specialty: text
- sections: jsonb NOT NULL
  -- Array of: {id: string, title: string, prompt: string, example: string, order: number}
- is_system: boolean DEFAULT false
- is_published: boolean DEFAULT false
- created_at: timestamptz DEFAULT now()
- updated_at: timestamptz DEFAULT now()
```

### audit_log
```sql
- id: uuid PK DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- user_id: uuid FK → users.id NOT NULL
- action: text NOT NULL (e.g., 'view_transcript', 'generate_note', 'export_note', 'finalize_note')
- resource_type: text NOT NULL (e.g., 'consultation', 'transcript', 'clinical_note')
- resource_id: uuid NOT NULL
- metadata: jsonb DEFAULT '{}'
- ip_address: inet
- created_at: timestamptz DEFAULT now()
```

## Row Level Security Patterns
- Every table with user_id uses: `auth.uid() = user_id`
- Audit log: insert-only for authenticated users, read by admins only
- Templates: users see system templates + their own
- Organization-level sharing via organization_id when teams are enabled

## Indexes
- consultations: (user_id, created_at DESC), (status), (patient_id)
- clinical_notes: (consultation_id), (status)
- transcripts: (consultation_id) UNIQUE
- audit_log: (user_id, created_at DESC), (resource_type, resource_id)
- patients: (user_id, mrn) UNIQUE
